        public static final java.lang.String TAG_AMEX_SET_QUALIFIERS
        Enhanced ContactLess Reader Capabilities. Tag : 9F6E.

        Byte 1
        b8 : 1 = EMV Contact Chip Supported.
        b7 : 1 = MSD Supported.
        b6 : 0 = (Fixed Parameter)

        b7 : 1 = Online PIN Supported.
        b6 : 1 = Signature Supported.

        Byte 3
        b8 : 1 = Terminal is Offline Only.
        b7 : 1 = CVM Required.
        b6-b1 : RFU. (000000)

        Byte 4

        b7 : 1 = Delayed Authorisations.
        RFU. ('00')
